\pard\tx3120\tx3620\tx4120\i0\fs28\li2620\fc0\cf0 Sets the factor by which the input signal is scaled.  By default, the scaler is set to 1.0.  Effective values are between 0.0 and 1.0 (negative values are the same as their absolute values, but with a 180 degree phase shift).  Returns 
